* Description

  This repository is for CM14.1 on Samsung X Cover 2 a.k.a Samsung Skomer.
  It's still a work in progress.

* How To Build

  - Make a workspace

  $ mkdir -p ~/lineage
  $ cd ~/lineage


  - Do repo init & sync

  $ repo init -u git://github.com/LineageOS/android.git -b cm-11.0


  - Create .repo/local_manifests/skomer.xml with the following content:

  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
  <manifest>
      <project name="shamu2811/android_device_samsung_skomer" path="device/samsung/skomer" />
      <project name="shamu2811/android_kernel_samsung_skomer" path="kernel/samsung/skomer" />
      <project name="shamu2811/android_vendor_samsung_skomer" path="vendor/samsung/skomer" />
  </manifest>

  $ repo sync


  - Setup vendor

  $ ./vendor/lineage/get-prebuilts


  - Pull all not merged fixes from gerrit:
  $ ./device/samsung/skomer/pull


  - Setup environment

  $ source build/envsetup.sh
  $ lunch lineage_skomer-eng


  - Build CM14.1

  $ export USE_CCACHE=1
  $ make -j4 skomer


